headline: Arista Networks Ups 2026 Outlook As AI Ethernet Growth Meets Valuation Gap
summary: Arista Networks (NYSE:ANET) has raised its 2026 revenue growth outlook, tied to accelerating demand for AI focused Ethernet switching. The company is gaining share in high speed data center networking as cloud providers increase spending on AI infrastructure. Arista is leaning on its open ecosystem model and ultra high speed switching portfolio to compete against legacy networking vendors. Arista’s move comes after a strong multi year share price run, with the stock up 35.1% over the past...
